<L>HARK! the bell, with doleful hum,</L>
<L>To the lagging cor&s;e cries <HI>come.</HI></L>
<L>To the lagging cor&s;e the bell,</L>
<L>Sounds, with doleful hum, this knell.</L>
<L>CABBAGINO, <HI>come away!</HI></L>
<L><HI>Ha&s;ten to thy kindred day!</HI></L>
<L><HI>To thy kindred day, O ha&s;te!</HI></L>
